        Patients who require intraoperative invasive arterial blood pressure monitoring.
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria: children under 10 years old how are diagnosed as

